beer.beer_name: In-Breed Westy Kong Hazelnut Brown Ale
beer.beer_description:
Do you dare climb the ladders of malt and hazelnut to achieve your highest
Brown Ale level?
This In-Breed comes courtesy of our resident barrel wrangler, Westy.
When he’s not wrangling barrels, he’s hurling them at love-struck Marios trying
to rescue damsels in distress. When he’s not doing either of those things he’s
brewing up luscious brown ales, just like this one.

APPEAR ANCE:
Rich, silky brown.
AROMA:
Toasted malt with subtle hazelnut notes.
Mild fruit esters with herbal, resinous
notes from the hops.
FL AVOUR:
Richly layered malt flavours of caramel,
toast, hazelnut, chocolate and coffee
with a moderately bitter finish.
